Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底的万圣节跟地面没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halloween is no different under the waves--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗  骷髅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pirates, skeletons
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有海怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sea monsters
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.08,0:01:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人玩得都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone having fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(461,426)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(775,566)}万圣节快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几乎所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, almost everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:25.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,886)}嘣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  盘子都洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Krabs, the dishes are done--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想听我一年一篇的鬼故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to hear my annual scary story?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了谢谢  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事里是不是有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does it have monsters in it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最最凶残的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The worst monster of them all
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.04,0:01:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真实发生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it a true story?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟大海一样真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,True as the deep blue
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我还是听一听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe just a little
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请坐下  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a seat, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每年  在万圣节前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every year, on Halloween night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.72,0:02:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼会驾着海盗船降临裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,descends on Bikini Bottom in a pirate ship
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多像这样  但是大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like this, only bigger
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.94,0:02:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的船样子是不是像蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did his ship look like a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正如我所说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like I was saying
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼会突然俯冲下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Flying Dutchman swoops down
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始偷取人们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and starts stealing people's souls
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灵魂的样子是不是很像腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do souls look like pickles?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  其实确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, as a matter of fact, they do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他会放到你绝对取不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he puts them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where you can never get them--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灵魂袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in his soul bag
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(883,510)}灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(867,790)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来取你腌椰菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've come for your pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝一年比一年好吓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scaredy-Pants gets easier to scare every year
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精彩的鬼故事效果就是好  对吧小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a good ghost story, eh, me boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你今晚来我这的派对可别被吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hope you're not too scared to come to me party tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷走你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steal your soul
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.96,0:03:09.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:09.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, son
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是胆小鬼海绵宝宝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节快乐  胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Halloween, Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The name's SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每年万圣节  不管我尽了多大的力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every Halloween, no matter how hard I try
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家还是会吓到我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everybody scares me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经烦透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sick of it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不再当胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  派大星来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, it's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去吓吓他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to scare him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my turn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.83,0:03:54.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:54.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不是有意要吓到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to scare you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么我一次都吓不到别人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't I be frightening for once?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的机会在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my chance?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想要吓人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to be scary
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要有套好的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to need a good costume
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打扮咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我的糖果袋刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going as my trick-or-treat bag
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the ghost of the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something's missing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快穿上吧  飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step into these babies, Hans
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terrifying
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不行  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有小孩子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's little kids
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子可好吓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little kids are easy to scare
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是闹鬼的床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's the haunted mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,糖果拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your candy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was enough of a treat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来看看我新做的纸幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, look at my new paper ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这个  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟那个幽灵有什么地方不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between that ghost and me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.38,0:05:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能答出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能答出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别说答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑袋是方的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a square head
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正幽灵的脑袋是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a real ghost has a round one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要让我的脑袋变圆  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is make my head round and--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就变可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  要弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的确定想这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刮我脑袋  让我变圆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shave me down, make me round
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始刮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get to it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打扮咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's scary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块去吓个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go scare somebody
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.14,0:06:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know who I am
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.49,0:06:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman's best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们小朋友不要糖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you kids want your candy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  刚才真是好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, that was something
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的打扮真的好有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your costume really packs a punch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No question
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把那家伙狠狠地吓着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You scared the barnacles off that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们接下来该吓谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who should we scare next?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王办了个派对  里面全都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a whole party just full of people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.15,0:07:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼要不请自来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the Flying Dutchman is going to show up uninvited
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes someone now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是刚才那个闹鬼床垫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the haunted mattress?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他估计是被贬成闹鬼睡袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he's been demoted to a haunted sleeping bag
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(531,256)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(629,206)}万圣节快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸  你又害得我好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dad, you're embarrassing me again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great party, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打扮的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是养在鱼缸里的宠物小金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm a pet goldfish in a bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kill the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.81,0:08:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你们的灵魂给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me your souls
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的便服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are my street clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flying Dutchman?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得叫飞天笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flying Dopeman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the real Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们胆小鬼看得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet your lily white livers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你们透露个小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll let you in on a little secret
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要偷取你们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to steal your soul
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你们自找的  大个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had it coming, you big crybabies
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每年人们都会打扮成我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every year, people dressing like me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把飞天魔鬼的名号变成了笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turning the Flying Dutchman name
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a laughingstock
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我要取走你们灵魂  并非因为那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's not the reason I'm taking your souls
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是这个成为了压垮骆驼的最后稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, this is the straw that broke the camel's back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我见过的所有飞天魔鬼打扮当中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of all the Dutchman costumes I've seen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就属你的最冒犯我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yours is the most insulting
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意思是不是我不吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mean I'm not scary?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我告诉你什么叫吓人  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you about scary, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界上有各种各样吓人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of scary things in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spiders are scary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not scary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  来把事情成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先我要把你这套破打扮摘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First I got to get rid of this stupid costume
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I scared him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吓到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I scared everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计是因为你的粉红色帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it was your pink hat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉红色帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my brain
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会长回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It grows back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.02,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,308)\fsp40}我是少年蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(319,322)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(417,676)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(399,280)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317,340)\frz21.11}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.11\pos(465,624)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锻炼时间结束了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exercise time is over, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能让你变太瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't want you getting too thin
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fetch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下去  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母年度大会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The annual jellyfish convention
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这周末要在尤克里里村举办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Ukulele bottom this weekend
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you ready or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这周末就要办吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was this weekend?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人帮我照顾小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone to take care of Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.40,0:13:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别再把你内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you please stop leaving your undergarments
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我庭院里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on my front lawn?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你这周末能帮忙看下小蜗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, could you watch Gary this weekend?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是只小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是只小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a Gary--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要叫小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的宠物蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's my pet snail
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "Hello"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你养的居然是这么个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You actually care for that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找别人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get somebody else
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来咱们周末没法走了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't go away this weekend after all, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.35,0:13:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说  要是我照看小蜗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, if I watch Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一整个周末都要走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you guys will be gone all weekend?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实咱这个周末有三天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, a three-day weekend
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是三天都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As in "Not here for three days"?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  不过你说过你不帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you've already said you can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.15,0:14:05.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:05.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We understand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要难过  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们三个还是能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The three of us can still have
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你家里自个儿办捉水母大会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our own jellyfish convention at your house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I changed my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们周末应该走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys deserve a weekend away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来给你教一下照顾蜗牛的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you a little bit about snail care
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一天要遛两次小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to take Gary for a walk twice a day
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.59,0:14:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周五周六还有周天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friday, Saturday and Sunday--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三天的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a three-day weekend
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教你要怎么喂小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how to feed him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(807,182)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把所有罐子都做了标记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have all the cans marked
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(977,298)}早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(949,752)}晚
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上一罐  晚上一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A can in the morning and a can at night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure it's enough?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus is here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bus is here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, time to go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't want to be late
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的指示你应该不会忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you won't forget my instructions, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我记性好得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the memory of an elephant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会照顾好小弗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, losers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这三天会是我一生中最美好的三天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the best three days of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要做完所有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do all the things
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝害我没法正常做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't normally do because of SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1005)}三天后
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.20,0:15:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生中最美好的周末就这样结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thus ends the greatest weekend of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝  没有派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No SpongeBob, no Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing but me, me, me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The snail
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘记蜗牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot the snail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(951.323,154)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1013.409,874)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来来来  就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go, here we go, right here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须把饭都吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to finish this food
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, eat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I'm home
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你检查一下小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,checking up on old Gary for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是个好朋友  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a great friend you are, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.49,0:16:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们等会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是能靠得住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can always count on you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, what's happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪里有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  小蜗出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, something's wrong with Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对  就跟我想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, it's just as I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这绝对是蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is definitely a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squid, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以  蜗牛血浆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Therefore, a shot of snail plasma
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要小心注射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,must be carefully administered
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要来注射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我晕针
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too squeamish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, doc
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你提包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with your bag there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法帮小蜗注射血浆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't give Gary his plasma
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也晕针
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm squeamish, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我可不想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I don't want to
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  我来注射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别伤着人家了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't hurt him, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  稳一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, steady
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.43,0:18:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.27,0:18:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold him still
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你抱着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hold him still
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把蜗牛血浆注射到我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've injected me with snail plasma
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你逼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you made me do it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没什么  一点蜗牛血浆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, it's just a little snail plasma
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说  我感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I feel kind of funny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是因为你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you it's all in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:36.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1181.643,930)}水
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意只是要水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just needed water?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary, you're better
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太感人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How touching
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回家去吐一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go home and throw up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥别走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛血浆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The snail plasma
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说我会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward says I'll be fine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他无所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He knows everything
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686.955,884)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat up, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉小蜗  我控制不住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Gary, I couldn't control myself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why'd I just do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要垮掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I cracking up?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  章鱼哥说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Squidward's right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.99,0:19:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I worry too much
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all in my head
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel tip-top
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你速度变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you're getting a lot faster
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好得不能再好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说我好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward said I'm fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我是左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a lefty, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我用不着买新鞋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to buy those new shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把话收回去  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I take it back, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.75,0:20:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望以后再也看不到蜗牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope I never see another snail again
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Clari
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会是谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得跟我不知道似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As if I didn't already know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我都跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I already told you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to be just fi--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  我都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune, what have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,集中精神  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我喂了蜗牛  这一切都不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,None of this would be happening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I'd only fed that snail
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们能不能安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you clam up?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了小鬼们  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boils and ghouls, you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:57.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的坟场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives near a graveyard under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄  吓人自如
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and spooky is he
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处受怕是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical chills be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就大声尖叫像大鱼弹跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then scream your gills out and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.62,0:23:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Scaredy-Pants
